    VerifyMatches extends Matches to provide some additional verification capabilities. It will handle all verifications performed on the actual element. These asserts are custom to the framework, and in addition to providing easy object oriented capabilities, they take screenshots with each verification to provide additional traceability, and assist in troubleshooting and debugging failing tests. Matches checks that elements have a particular value associated to them that fits the provided regular expression.
